        "javadoc": "/**\n * Creates a Predicate that checks if the input object is equal to the\n * specified object using equals().\n *\n * @param <T>  the type that the predicate queries\n * @param value  the value to compare against\n * @return the predicate\n * @see EqualPredicate\n */\n",
